&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
コロナウイルスの非常事態宣言のため、静かで穏やかな二年坂の午後。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><summary type="html">A quiet afternoon on the usually busy Ninenzaka, thanks to the latest Coronavirus State of Emergency.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2104_A7R05835.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Temple Blooms・寺の花</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210426/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Temple Blooms・寺の花" /><published>2021-04-26T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-04-26T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/temple-blooms</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210426/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Small lotus blossoms are blooming at Kaju-ji Temple in Yamashina, along with irises behind.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
山科の勧修寺では小さなハスの花が咲き、背後には菖蒲が咲いています。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Gardens" /><category term="Flowers" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html">Small lotus blossoms are blooming at Kaju-ji Temple in Yamashina, along with irises behind.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2104_A7R05765.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Irises at Umenomiya Taisha・梅宮大社のアヤメ</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210425/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Irises at Umenomiya Taisha・梅宮大社のアヤメ" /><published>2021-04-25T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-04-25T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/umenomiya</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210425/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Although mostly known for their plum trees, Umenomiya Taisha Shrine also has many irises, now starting to bloom.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
梅宮大社は梅の花で有名ですが、菖蒲もたくさんあります。 彼らは咲き始めています。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Gardens" /><category term="Shrines" /><summary type="html">Although mostly known for their plum trees, Umenomiya Taisha Shrine also has many irises, now starting to bloom.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2104_IMG_3111.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Kenrokuen Garden・兼六園</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210424/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kenrokuen Garden・兼六園" /><published>2021-04-24T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-04-24T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kenrokuen</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210424/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
