日本海の夕焼け、輪島市から。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Water" /><summary type="html">Last light on the Sea of Japan, in the town of Wajima.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2104_A7R05701.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Wajima Sunset・輪島の夕暮れ</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210422/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Wajima Sunset・輪島の夕暮れ" /><published>2021-04-22T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-04-22T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/wajimasunset</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210422/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Sunset on the Sea of Japan. Overlooking the Kamogaura rocks at Sodegahama Beach in Wajima, Ishikawa Prefecture.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
日本海の夕暮れ。 輪島の鴨ヶ浦。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Water" /><summary type="html">Sunset on the Sea of Japan. Overlooking the Kamogaura rocks at Sodegahama Beach in Wajima, Ishikawa Prefecture.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2104_A7R05677-HDR.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Morning Sea・朝の海</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210421/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Morning Sea・朝の海" /><published>2021-04-21T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-04-21T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/fisherman</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210421/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
A fishing boat returns to port after an early morning. In the distance are oyster farms.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
早朝、漁から港に戻る漁船。 遠くにカキの養殖場がある。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Water" /><summary type="html">A fishing boat returns to port after an early morning. In the distance are oyster farms.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2104_A7R05521.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Chaya Bijin・茶屋美人</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210420/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Chaya Bijin・茶屋美人" /><published>2021-04-20T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-04-20T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kanazawa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210420/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
A row of 19th century tea houses in Kanazawa’s Higashi Chaya District, where Geisha still entertain.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
金沢のひがし茶屋街にある並ぶ19世紀の茶屋。芸妓は今でも芸を披露しています。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html">A row of 19th century tea houses in Kanazawa’s Higashi Chaya District, where Geisha still entertain.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2104_A7R05419.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Nagaoka Tenjin・長岡天神</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210419/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Nagaoka Tenjin・長岡天神" /><published>2021-04-19T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-04-19T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/nagaoka</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210419/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Red azaleas blooming at Nagaoka Tenjin Shrine.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
長岡天神に咲く紅つつじ。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Flowers" /><category term="Shrines" /><summary type="html">Red azaleas blooming at Nagaoka Tenjin Shrine.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2104_A7R05378.jpg" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Kyoto Clouds・京都の夕焼け</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210417/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kyoto Clouds・京都の夕焼け" /><published>2021-04-17T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2021-04-17T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/sunset</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/210417/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
After a day of rain, the clouds broke and I raced up to Kyoto Tower to capture some of the beautiful evening sky.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
雨の日の後、太陽が出てきました。 美しい夕方の空を撮影するために京都タワーに行きました。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Clouds" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Aerial" /><summary type="html">After a day of rain, the clouds broke and I raced up to Kyoto Tower to capture some of the beautiful evening sky.</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2104_IMG_2999.jpg" /></entry></feed>